    "description": {
      "zh": "Staccato XC融合了1911式手枪的精准与现代创新设计，配备双排弹匣、可加装瞄具的套筒、双侧保险以及集成皮卡汀尼导轨。聚合物握把与锻钢框架确保卓越性能与可靠性，使其成为竞技射击的首选利器。",
      "en": "The Staccato XC blends the precision of a 1911 with modern innovation, featuring a double-stack magazine, optics-ready slide, ambidextrous safety, and an integrated Picatinny rail. Its polymer grip and forged steel frame ensure superior performance and reliability, making it a top choice for competitive shooting."
